She watched as Stringtra stormed off.
Things were looking bad and she had a huntch that it was about to get 
worse.

She ran back to the base and right up to Wildfire. "I need you to 
tell me what is out htere and tell me now.  KitKat is at the cave and 
Stringtra just ran off out there and is who knows where.  Just what 
is it that we are up against.  What has affected Quickstrick and and 
what is out there and what are we dealing with? I need answers and I 
need them now!"
